article_title: Goldman Sachs Partners Cut Combined Ownership Stake to 8.52%
article_text:
Goldman Sachs Group Inc.'s senior-most employees have sold about 4.93 million shares of the Wall Street firm since late May, lowering their combined ownership stake to 8.52%.

Goldman's 409 partners held about 38.66 million shares as of Aug. 13, the New York firm said Friday in a regulatory filing. In a previous filing, the group's stake totaled...
